les\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4216}, {\"ngram\": \"royalty\", \"from\": 4220, \"to\": 4227}, {\"ngram\": \"nobility\", \"from\": 4232, \"to\": 4240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the witty imagery from Shonda Rimes' Shondaland, which has won over millions of viewers worldwide.\", \"from\": 4243, \"to\": 4349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4274, \"end\": 4286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shonda_Rhimes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shonda Rimes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shonda_Rhimes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shonda_Rhimes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the witty imagery\", \"from\": 4251, \"to\": 4268}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 4319, \"to\": 4327}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And why not?\", \"from\": 4350, \"to\": 4362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of those grand buildings and events were created by the sweat of millions of enslaved Africans.\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4445, \"end\": 4462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slavery_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.6286040365909538, \"rank\": 0.5884565347098112, \"text\": \"enslaved Africans\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slavery_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slavery_in_the_United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those grand buildings\", \"from\": 4371, \"to\": 4392}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 4397, \"to\": 4403}, {\"ngram\": \"the sweat\", \"from\": 4420, \"to\": 4429}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 4433, \"to\": 4441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of the precious metals and jewels which had brought sparkle to such occasions were plundered from former colonies.\", \"from\": 4464, \"to\": 4583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the precious metals\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4491}, {\"ngram\": \"jewels\", \"from\": 4496, \"to\": 4502}, {\"ngram\": \"sparkle\", \"from\": 4521, \"to\": 4528}, {\"ngram\": \"such occasions\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4546}, {\"ngram\": \"former colonies\", \"from\": 4567, \"to\": 4582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first look at the variegated cast may have been surprising, but as the seasons progressed, we have found them to be natural and believable.\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first look\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4599}, {\"ngram\": \"the variegated cast\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4622}, {\"ngram\": \"the seasons\", \"from\": 4656, \"to\": 4667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This took me back to a speech made by the late Professor Rex Nettleford to the advertising fraternity in the 80s: \\\"I understand that the explanation for so many light-skinned people appearing in advertisements is that the lighting suits them better,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4729, \"to\": 4988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4786, \"end\": 4800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rex_Nettleford\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rex Nettleford\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rex_Nettleford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rex_Nettleford\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a speech\", \"from\": 4750, \"to\": 4758}, {\"ngram\": \"the advertising fraternity\", \"from\": 4804, \"to\": 4830}, {\"ngram\": \"the 80s\", \"from\": 4834, \"to\": 4841}, {\"ngram\": \"the explanation\", \"from\": 4862, \"to\": 4877}, {\"ngram\": \"so many light-skinned people\", \"from\": 4882, \"to\": 4910}, {\"ngram\": \"advertisements\", \"from\": 4924, \"to\": 4938}, {\"ngram\": \"the lighting\", \"from\": 4947, \"to\": 4959}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, I challenge you all to fix the lighting!\\\"\", \"from\": 4989, \"to\": 5037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lighting\", \"from\": 5023, \"to\": 5035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shondaland has not only fixed the lighting but has also given us a world free of racism, a world we all hope to see one day.\", \"from\": 5039, \"to\": 5163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5039, \"end\": 5049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shonda_Rhimes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7896601164332955e-17, \"text\": \"Shondaland\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shonda_Rhimes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shonda_Rhimes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lighting\", \"from\": 5069, \"to\": 5081}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5101, \"to\": 5103}, {\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 5104, \"to\": 5111}, {\"ngram\": \"racism\", \"from\": 5120, \"to\": 5126}, {\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 5128, \"to\": 5135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Farewell, Kingsley Cooper Jamaica is reeling from the loss of cultural and entertainment icon Kingsley Cooper.\", \"from\": 5167, \"to\": 5278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5177, \"end\": 5185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Kingsley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.775237175038912e-28, \"text\": \"Kingsley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Kingsley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Kingsley\"}, {\"begin\": 5194, \"end\": 5201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9288654436326495e-19, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 5262, \"end\": 5270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Kingsley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.775237175038912e-28, \"text\": \"Kingsley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Kingsley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Kingsley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the loss\", \"from\": 5217, \"to\": 5225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With his passing have come tributes from not only government leaders but also from the myriad organisations and individuals who were inspired and mentored by him.\", \"from\": 5279, \"to\": 5441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tributes\", \"from\": 5306, \"to\": 5314}, {\"ngram\": \"not only government leaders\", \"from\": 5320, \"to\": 5347}, {\"ngram\": \"the myriad organisations\", \"from\": 5362, \"to\": 5386}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 5391, \"to\": 5402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks to television host Alrick McKenzie, we heard Cooper relate his life story just seven months ago: his love of art; being appointed head boy of his beloved alma mater, Kingston College; and his extra-curricular activities while he studied law at The University of the West Indies.\", \"from\": 5443, \"to\": 5728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5616, \"end\": 5632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Thames_Colleges_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.778210620077403e-20, \"text\": \"Kingston College\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Thames_Colleges_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Thames_Colleges_Group\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"television host\", \"from\": 5453, \"to\": 5468}, {\"ngram\": \"Alrick McKenzie\", \"from\": 5469, \"to\": 5484}, {\"ngram\": \"Cooper\", \"from\": 5495, \"to\": 5501}, {\"ngram\": \"his life story\", \"from\": 5509, \"to\": 5523}, {\"ngram\": \"his love\", \"from\": 5547, \"to\": 5555}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 5559, \"to\": 5562}, {\"ngram\": \"head boy\", \"from\": 5580, \"to\": 5588}, {\"ngram\": \"his beloved alma mater\", \"from\": 5592, \"to\": 5614}, {\"ngram\": \"his extra-curricular activities\", \"from\": 5638, \"to\": 5669}, {\"ngram\": \"law\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5690}, {\"ngram\": \"The University\", \"from\": 5694, \"to\": 5708}, {\"ngram\": \"the West Indies\", \"from\": 5712, \"to\": 5727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said that the building of Pulse Investments Limited is a natural response to his God-given gifts, sharing that everyone has their unique gifts and we are called to develop them.\", \"from\": 5729, \"to\": 5909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the building\", \"from\": 5742, \"to\": 5754}, {\"ngram\": \"Pulse Investments Limited\", \"from\": 5758, \"to\": 5783}, {\"ngram\": \"a natural response\", \"from\": 5787, \"to\": 5805}, {\"ngram\": \"his God-given gifts\", \"from\": 5809, \"to\": 5828}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 5843, \"to\": 5851}, {\"ngram\": \"their unique gifts\", \"from\": 5856, \"to\": 5874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In developing his gifts, he brought new opportunities for aspiring models, who, under his guidance, have graced the covers ofVogueand catwalks at international shows.\", \"from\": 5911, \"to\": 6077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his gifts\", \"from\": 5925, \"to\": 5934}, {\"ngram\": \"new opportunities\", \"from\": 5947, \"to\": 5964}, {\"ngram\": \"aspiring models\", \"from\": 5969, \"to\": 5984}, {\"ngram\": \"his guidance\", \"from\": 5997, \"to\": 6009}, {\"ngram\": \"the covers\", \"from\": 6023, \"to\": 6033}, {\"ngram\": \"catwalks\", \"from\": 6045, \"to\": 6053}, {\"ngram\": \"international shows\", \"from\": 6057, \"to\": 6076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He developed his Pulse headquarters on Trafalgar Road into a hub of fashion and entertainment and booked internationally acclaimed artistes to perform at big shows, taking disappointing no-shows as lessons in building his business.\", \"from\": 6078, \"to\": 6309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6117, \"end\": 6126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trafalgar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7453311970454623e-22, \"text\": \"Trafalgar\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trafalgar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_Trafalgar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his Pulse headquarters\", \"from\": 6091, \"to\": 6113}, {\"ngram\": \"a hub\", \"from\": 6137, \"to\": 6142}, {\"ngram\": \"fashion\", \"from\": 6146, \"to\": 6153}, {\"ngram\": \"entertainment\", \"from\": 6158, \"to\": 6171}, {\"ngram\": \"internationally acclaimed artistes\", \"from\": 6183, \"to\": 6217}, {\"ngram\": \"big shows\", \"from\": 6232, \"to\": 6241}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointing no-shows\", \"from\": 6250, \"to\": 6272}, {\"ngram\": \"lessons\", \"from\": 6276, \"to\": 6283}, {\"ngram\": \"his business\", \"from\": 6296, \"to\": 6308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By gaining the confidence of investors, Cooper listed Pulse Investments on the Jamaica Stock Exchange and expanded into real estate development, transforming Villa Ronai into an elegant residential and commercial complex.\", \"from\": 6311, \"to\": 6532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6390, \"end\": 6412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Stock_Exchange\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamaica Stock Exchange\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Stock_Exchange\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Stock_Exchange\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the confidence\", \"from\": 6322, \"to\": 6336}, {\"ngram\": \"investors\", \"from\": 6340, \"to\": 6349}, {\"ngram\": \"Cooper\", \"from\": 6351, \"to\": 6357}, {\"ngram\": \"Pulse Investments\", \"from\": 6365, \"to\": 6382}, {\"ngram\": \"real estate development\", \"from\": 6431, \"to\": 6454}, {\"ngram\": \"Villa Ronai\", \"from\": 6469, \"to\": 6480}, {\"ngram\": \"an elegant residential and commercial complex\", \"from\": 6486, \"to\": 6531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It all seemed so natural for this nationalist, but it must have taken extraordinary effort during the 40-year ebb and flow of the economy.\", \"from\": 6533, \"to\": 6671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_